\";s:28:\"review-pmpro-over-100-orders\";s:6:\"starts\";s:10:\"2020-01-22\";s:4:\"ends\";s:10:\"2030-01-01\";s:8:\"priority\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"show_if\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:16:\"pmpro_num_orders\";a:2:{i:0;s:1:\">\";i:1;s:3:\"100\";}}s:4:\"type\";s:7:\"general\";s:8:\"dashicon\";s:11:\"star-filled\";s:5:\"title\";s:44:\"Please take a moment to rate & review PMPro.\";s:7:\"content\";s:376:\"<p>Hi there! You\'ve recently hit 100 orders on your PMPro-powered membership site - that\'s awesome!! If you\'d like to celebrate this milestone, would you mind rating us 5-stars to help spread the word?</p><p><a class=\"button button-primary\" target=\"blank\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/paid-memberships-pro/reviews/?filter=5#new-post\">Okay, you deserve it</a></p>\";s:11:\"dismissable\";b:1;}i:5;O:8:\"stdClass\":11:{s:2:\"id\";i:40101;s:4:\"name\";s:22:\"install-sitewide-sales\";s:6:\"starts\";s:10:\"2023-08-15\";s:4:\"ends\";s:10:\"2023-11-15\";s:8:\"priority\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"hide_if\";O:8:\"stdClass\":1:{s:14:\"plugins_active\";a:1:{i:0;s:33:\"sitewide-sales/sitewide-sales.php\";}}s:4:\"type\";s:7:\"general\";s:8:\"dashicon\";s:4:\"cart\";s:5:\"title\";s:70:\"Run Black Friday or Cyber Monday Sales in PMPro, WooCommerce, and EDD.\";s:7:\"content\";s:559:\"<p>The <a target=\"blank\" href=\"https://www.sitewidesales.com/?utm_source=plugin&utm_medium=pmpro-notifications&utm_campaign=sitewide-sales&utm_content=40101\">Sitewide Sales plugin</a> handles your discounts, banners, landing pages, and reporting. Check out this new all-in-one tool that helps ecommerce or membership sites run better sales.</p><p><a class=\"button button-primary\" target=\"blank\" href=\"https://www.sitewidesales.com/?utm_source=plugin&utm_medium=pmpro-notifications&utm_campaign=sitewide-sales&utm_content=40101\">Visit SitewideSales.com</a></p>\";s:11:\"dismissable\";b:1;}i:6;O:8:\"stdClass\":12:{s:2:\"id\";i:40102;s:4:\"name\";s:33:\"install-pmpro-bbpress-integration\";s:6:\"starts\";s:10